sources.description:
Battle of the Bulge: Wunderland - Winter 1944, Army Lt. Robert Cappa and his platoon of 2nd Infantry Division soldiers have been ordered to hold a vital road junction against the first stages of an attacking German Army in the epic Battle of the War known as "The Battle of the Bulge."
2018.  Stars: Steven Luke, Tom Berenger, Mikeal Burgin
